{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6a5b99366a","title":"致鼓荣臻、萧克、刘澜涛等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e8c17a4de3","index":0,"year":1946,"month":9,"day":6,"articleId":"6a5b99366a"}],"tags":[{"id":"3dcf7883ce","name":"刘澜涛","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6bca5c7ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"致鼓荣臻、萧克、刘澜涛等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"6a5b99366a"},{"id":"54fa8a09b8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年9月6日）绥傅叫大举进攻，必须集中优势兵力迅速歼灭该敌。此战役归你们总负责，如何部署，速告。[1]这是毛泽东为中央军委起草的致爱荣臻、萧克、刘润涛并告张宗遇、罗瑞卿电的主要内容。7日，楚荣臻、萧克复电中央军委：“傅顽东犯，尚不能取得东西两面之直接配合，我先集中力量打傅项与继续围攻大同，尚属有利。”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"6a5b99366a"}],"page":{"id":"afea145f47","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"6a5b99366a","start":136,"end":136}}}},"__N_SSG":true}